F(x)= \ln\left(x+\sqrt{4+x^2}\right)
\dfrac{1}{\sqrt{4+x^2}}
\dfrac{\sqrt{4+x^2}+x}{x\sqrt{4+x^2}+4+x^2}
\dfrac{d}{dx}[\ln(f(x))] = \dfrac{f'(x)}{f(x)}
f(x) = x + \sqrt{4 + x^2} = x + (4 + x^2)^{\frac{1}{2}}
f'(x) = 1 + \frac{1}{2}(4 + x^2)^{-\frac{1}{2}}\cdot (2x) = 1 + x(4 + x^2)^{-\frac{1}{2}}
f'(x)
f(x)
\sqrt{4 + x^2}
\begin{aligned} F'(x) = \dfrac{\color{red}{f'(x)}}{\color{blue}{f(x)}} &= \dfrac{\color{red}{1 + x(4 + x^2)^{-\frac{1}{2}}}}{\color{blue}{x + \sqrt{4 + x^2}}} & \text{[Use $f'(x)$ and $f(x)$]}\\ &= \dfrac{1 + \frac{x}{\sqrt{4 + x^2}}}{x + \sqrt{4 + x^2}}\\ &= \dfrac{\sqrt{4 + x^2} + x}{(x + \sqrt{4 + x^2})\cdot \sqrt{4 + x^2}} & \text{[Multiply top and bottom by $\sqrt{4 + x^2}$]}\\ &= \color{green}{\dfrac{\sqrt{4 + x^2} + x}{x\sqrt{4 + x^2} + 4 + x^2}} \end{aligned}
